schools.name: Dr. Claude G Perkins Elementary School

data.description: This home features a great open floor plan, 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths, vaulted ceilings and ceiling fans through out. Living Room is open and spacious w/ a cozy fireplace. Kitchen has granite counter tops and a breakfast nook and a large gathering area (family room). Primary bedroom is large, open and spacious w/ a walk in closet. Pool size lot , patio cover and 2 car garage. Centrally Located, close to schools, parks, shopping and easy access to the freeway. Close to Downtown Art District and Culinary Academy of Las Vegas
